com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class TagOutOfOrderException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.camerontec.catalys.core.message.AbstractMessageException
          • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.TagOutOfOrderException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TagOutOfOrderException
extends AbstractMessageException
    Indicates receiving FIX message with MsgType field not at the third position. In non-trusted mode(or "trusted" mode but with dialectIgnoreTagOrdering is off) the Logout would be sent in reply to such FIX message if it's Logon and Reject in case of any other messages.
    See Also:
